    <title>我的博客搭建记录</title>
    <link href="http://example.com/2025/07/12/%E6%88%91%E7%9A%84%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%B0%E5%BD%95/"/>
    <id>http://example.com/2025/07/12/%E6%88%91%E7%9A%84%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%B0%E5%BD%95/</id>
    <published>2025-07-12T07:44:06.000Z</published>
    <updated>2025-07-23T15:53:10.659Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>欢迎来到我的 Hexo 博客！</p><p>这是我的第一篇文章，使用 Butterfly 主题，非常漂亮！</p><h3 id="之前"><a href="#之前" class="headerlink" title="之前"></a>之前</h3><p>本人之前搭建由于未及时记录，已几近损失，此时为求长远搭建，时时更新，故作此篇，以录历程</p><h3 id="搜索"><a href="#搜索" class="headerlink" title="搜索"></a>搜索</h3><p>可以直接参考这个博主:</p><p><a href="https://www.mebi.me/hexo-with-algolia">hexo博客使用algolia搜索</a></p><h4 id="✅-什么是-Algolia-搜索？"><a href="#✅-什么是-Algolia-搜索？" class="headerlink" title="✅ 什么是 Algolia 搜索？"></a>✅ 什么是 Algolia 搜索？</h4><p><a href="https://www.algolia.com/">Algolia</a> 是一个提供快速、强大全文搜索服务的平台。Hexo + Algolia 可以实现比本地搜索（local search）更快更智能的搜索体验，尤其适合文章较多的博客。</p><hr><h4 id="✅-一、安装插件"><a href="#✅-一、安装插件" class="headerlink" title="✅ 一、安装插件"></a>✅ 一、安装插件</h4><p>在博客根目录打开终端，安装以下其中一个插件：</p><p><strong>使用 <code>hexo-algoliasearch</code>：</strong></p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm install hexo-algoliasearch --save</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><hr><h4 id="✅-二、配置-fields-字段（很重要）"><a href="#✅-二、配置-fields-字段（很重要）" class="headerlink" title="✅ 二、配置 fields 字段（很重要）"></a>✅ 二、配置 <code>fields</code> 字段（很重要）</h4><h5 id="Algolia-配置完整步骤详解"><a href="#Algolia-配置完整步骤详解" class="headerlink" title="Algolia 配置完整步骤详解"></a>Algolia 配置完整步骤详解</h5><hr><h6 id="1-注册-Algolia-账号"><a href="#1-注册-Algolia-账号" class="headerlink" title="1. 注册 Algolia 账号"></a>1. 注册 Algolia 账号</h6><ul><li>访问官网：<a href="https://www.algolia.com/">https://www.algolia.com/</a></li><li>点击右上角“Sign up”注册账号</li></ul><hr><h6 id="2-创建一个新的索引（Index）"><a href="#2-创建一个新的索引（Index）" class="headerlink" title="2. 创建一个新的索引（Index）"></a>2. 创建一个新的索引（Index）</h6><ul><li>登录后，在控制台首页点击 <strong>“New Application”</strong>（新建应用）</li><li>输入一个应用名称，比如：<code>my-blog-search</code></li><li>创建完成后进入这个应用管理页面</li><li>点击左侧菜单的 <strong>“Indices”</strong>，点击 <strong>“Add new index”</strong></li><li>输入索引名称，比如：<code>hexo_blog_index</code>，点击确认</li></ul><hr><h6 id="3-获取-API-Key-和-App-ID"><a href="#3-获取-API-Key-和-App-ID" class="headerlink" title="3. 获取 API Key 和 App ID"></a>3. 获取 API Key 和 App ID</h6><ul><li>在 Algolia 控制台，点击左侧的 <strong>“API Keys”</strong> 菜单</li><li>你会看到：</li></ul><table><thead><tr><th>名称</th><th>说明</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>Application ID</td><td>App ID，Hexo 配置中用到</td></tr><tr><td>Write API Key</td><td>管理权限密钥，用于上传数据</td></tr><tr><td>Search API Key</td><td>用于前端搜索，权限有限</td></tr></tbody></table><h5 id="配置-fields-字段"><a href="#配置-fields-字段" class="headerlink" title="配置 fields 字段"></a>配置 <code>fields</code> 字段</h5><p>你可以 Ctrl+F 搜索 “theme:”，然后把 algoliasearch 放在它下面：</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">theme: butterfly</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">algolia:</span><br><span class="line">  appId: &quot;WSRIBS46CE&quot;</span><br><span class="line">  apiKey: &quot;5f200c7783751675302f5d749932422d&quot;</span><br><span class="line">  adminApiKey: &quot;a6ac0b6a84dfd084b76b97970b6aa685&quot;</span><br><span class="line">  chunkSize: 5000</span><br><span class="line">  indexName: &quot;hexo_blog_index&quot;</span><br><span class="line">  fields:</span><br><span class="line">    - content:strip:truncate,0,500</span><br><span class="line">    - excerpt:strip</span><br><span class="line">    - gallery</span><br><span class="line">    - permalink</span><br><span class="line">    - photos</span><br><span class="line">    - slug</span><br><span class="line">    - tags</span><br><span class="line">    - title</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><blockquote><p>说明：</p><ul><li><code>appId</code>、<code>apiKey</code>、<code>indexName</code> 这些你需要在 Algolia 官网后台创建一个索引获取。</li><li><code>fields</code>：指定上传到 Algolia 的字段，<code>title</code>、<code>permalink</code> 和 <code>content</code> 是最基本的。</li></ul></blockquote><hr><h4 id="✅-三、配置-Butterfly-主题支持-Algolia"><a href="#✅-三、配置-Butterfly-主题支持-Algolia" class="headerlink" title="✅ 三、配置 Butterfly 主题支持 Algolia"></a>✅ 三、配置 Butterfly 主题支持 Algolia</h4><p>在主题配置文件 <code>_config.butterfly.yml</code> 中添加或修改：</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">search:</span><br><span class="line">  # Choose: algolia_search / local_search / docsearch</span><br><span class="line">  use: algolia_search</span><br><span class="line">  placeholder: 搜索文章关键词...</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">  # Algolia Search</span><br><span class="line">  algolia_search:</span><br><span class="line">    hitsPerPage: 6</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>然后添加：</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">algolia_search:</span><br><span class="line">  hitsPerPage: 6   # 搜索结果每页显示数量，可调</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><hr><h4 id="✅-四、生成索引并上传到-Algolia"><a href="#✅-四、生成索引并上传到-Algolia" class="headerlink" title="✅ 四、生成索引并上传到 Algolia"></a>✅ 四、生成索引并上传到 Algolia</h4><p>运行以下命令（注意顺序）：（如果你用的是 <code>hexo-algolia</code>）：</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo algolia</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>这一步会把你的博客内容上传到 Algolia 的服务器。</p><hr><h4 id="✅-五、部署并测试"><a href="#✅-五、部署并测试" class="headerlink" title="✅ 五、部署并测试"></a>✅ 五、部署并测试</h4><p>执行部署命令：</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo d</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>然后访问你的网站，在搜索框中尝试搜索关键字，应该会看到 Algolia 返回的实时结果。</p><hr><p>折腾了一整个下午，终于把 Hexo 和 Algolia 搜索搞定了。看似简单的几行配置，实则每一个字段名都可能藏着坑。最开始报错看不懂、路径出错、插件搞混、API Key 放错……真的是一边查文档一边试错，有时候一个缩进都能搞得人抓狂。</p><p>但也正是这种“踩坑→解决→继续”的过程，才是折腾的意义吧。看着搜索框终于能响应关键词、Algolia 返回的数据瞬间加载出来的那一刻，有种“技术点亮生活”的小小成就感。</p><p>这让我想起刚开始接触前端的时候，能让页面动起来就觉得很酷。现在一步步集成第三方搜索服务、改配置、部署上线，每一步都走得更稳了。</p><p>虽然花了不少时间，但换来的是更多信心：以后遇到问题，不怕了，查查文档、调调代码，总能解决。</p><p>每每出现问题，我都想起sing，我们好久没见面了，下午的时候一直在想她，（（她应该不会看到我这段话吧?__?））</p><h3 id="分享"><a href="#分享" class="headerlink" title="分享"></a>分享</h3><p><a href="https://github.com/overtrue/share.js/?tab=readme-ov-file#%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85">Share.js源代码</a></p><h4 id="安装"><a href="#安装" class="headerlink" title="安装"></a>安装</h4><p>使用 npm</p><p>npm install social-share.js</p><h4 id="使用（直接将以下代码放在文章末尾即可）"><a href="#使用（直接将以下代码放在文章末尾即可）" class="headerlink" title="使用（直接将以下代码放在文章末尾即可）"></a>使用（直接将以下代码放在文章末尾即可）</h4><figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">div</span> <span class="attr">class</span>=<span class="string">&quot;social-share&quot;</span>&gt;</span><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">div</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">&lt;!--  css &amp; js --&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">link</span> <span class="attr">rel</span>=<span class="string">&quot;stylesheet&quot;</span> <span class="attr">href</span>=<span class="string">&quot;dist/css/share.min.css&quot;</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">script</span> <span class="attr">src</span>=<span class="string">&quot;dist/js/social-share.min.js&quot;</span>&gt;</span><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">script</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">// 当你使用类名为 `social-share` 时不需要手动初始化</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>这个倒是很顺利</p><h3 id="评论"><a href="#评论" class="headerlink" title="评论"></a>评论</h3><p>参考此文章：</p><p><a href="https://jachinzhang1.github.io/2025/02/04/hexo%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E6%B7%BB%E5%8A%A0%E8%AF%84%E8%AE%BA%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F/">hexo博客添加评论系统</a></p><h4 id="安装-1"><a href="#安装-1" class="headerlink" title="安装"></a>安装</h4><p>进入Giscus的<a href="https://github.com/apps/giscus">安装界面</a>点击install安装</p><h4 id="官网配置"><a href="#官网配置" class="headerlink" title="官网配置"></a><a href="https://giscus.app/zh-CN">官网</a>配置</h4><p>选择一个GitHub仓库用于储存评论数据。</p><ol><li>该仓库是<strong>公开的</strong>；</li><li>giscus app 已安装；</li><li>Discussions 功能<strong>已在你的仓库中启用</strong>。 进入对应的仓库，点击右上角的 <code>Settings</code>，往下翻到<code>Features</code>，勾选<code>Discussions</code>。</li></ol><h4 id="个性化设置"><a href="#个性化设置" class="headerlink" title="个性化设置"></a>个性化设置</h4><p>【页面 &lt;-&gt; Discussion映射关系】 </p><p>建议选择title</p><p>【Discussion分类】 </p><p>建议选择<code>Announcements</code>，并勾选下面的“只搜索该分类中的discussion”</p><p>【特性】 </p><p>建议勾选“启用主帖子上的反应（可以给博客文章贴表情）”，“将评论框放在评论上方”和“懒加载评论（评论的加载将延迟到用户滚动到评论容器附近，有助于博客界面的快速加载，是一种前端显示的优化手段）”</p><p>【主题】 </p><p>建议勾选“用户偏好的色彩方案”</p><h4 id="启用giscus"><a href="#启用giscus" class="headerlink" title="启用giscus"></a>启用giscus</h4><p>完成上述设置之后，下面会自动生成对应的javascript代码。比如：</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&lt;script src=&quot;https://giscus.app/client.js&quot;</span><br><span class="line">        data-repo=&quot;jachinzhang1/jachinzhang1.github.io&quot;</span><br><span class="line">        data-repo-id=&quot;R_kgDONy_q0w&quot;</span><br><span class="line">        data-category=&quot;Announcements&quot;</span><br><span class="line">        data-category-id=&quot;DIC_kwDONy_q084Cmo0P&quot;</span><br><span class="line">        data-mapping=&quot;title&quot;</span><br><span class="line">        data-strict=&quot;0&quot;</span><br><span class="line">        data-reactions-enabled=&quot;1&quot;</span><br><span class="line">        data-emit-metadata=&quot;0&quot;</span><br><span class="line">        data-input-position=&quot;top&quot;</span><br><span class="line">        data-theme=&quot;preferred_color_scheme&quot;</span><br><span class="line">        data-lang=&quot;zh-CN&quot;</span><br><span class="line">        data-loading=&quot;lazy&quot;</span><br><span class="line">        crossorigin=&quot;anonymous&quot;</span><br><span class="line">        async&gt;</span><br><span class="line">&lt;/script&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>依照这个配置butterfly_config.yml的这里即可</p><figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># Giscus</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># https://giscus.app/</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">giscus:</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">repo:</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">repo_id:</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">category_id:</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">theme:</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">light:</span> <span class="string">light</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">dark:</span> <span class="string">dark</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">option:</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><hr><p>这个还是挺艰难的，弄了我将近一个钟，话说sing今天去广州看病了，今天上班一天都魂不守舍，蛮担心sing的，下午听到她医生说可以不用手术还是松了一气，而且晚上斯英主动找我聊天，超高兴的</p><h3 id="在线聊天"><a href="#在线聊天" class="headerlink" title="在线聊天"></a>在线聊天</h3><p>此功能因暂无需求，故不着意建立</p><hr><p>今天真的好忙，sing很想海达，打着电话的时候忍不住伤感，越是到见面前越是难忍，sing偷偷抹小眼泪时最让人心疼</p><h3 id="分析统计"><a href="#分析统计" class="headerlink" title="分析统计"></a>分析统计</h3><p>看起来还要审核什么的，好麻烦，故先放一边</p><h3 id="广告"><a href="#广告" class="headerlink" title="广告"></a>广告</h3><p>在我未接广告之前，应该时不会弄了</p><h3 id="网站验证"><a href="#网站验证" class="headerlink" title="网站验证"></a>网站验证</h3><p>就是让别人不用网址直接搜名字也能搜到，这个夜放后考虑。</p><h3 id="页面加载动画-preloader"><a href="#页面加载动画-preloader" class="headerlink" title="页面加载动画 preloader"></a>页面加载动画 preloader</h3><p>参考此片笔记：</p><p><a href="https://blog.meta-code.top/2022/06/18/2022-73/#%E4%BA%8C%E3%80%81%E5%88%9B%E5%BB%BA%E5%8A%A8%E7%94%BB%E7%BB%93%E6%9E%84%E6%A8%A1%E6%9D%BF%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6%E5%A4%B9">自定义Butterfly主题 Loading 加载动画</a></p><p>页面因尚未加装快速加载工具，时而缓慢显现，倘若有一加载动画，则有趣许多,以下内容皆为参考上篇笔记总结写出。</p><h4 id="序："><a href="#序：" class="headerlink" title="序："></a>序：</h4><p>由于本篇幅较其他较长，涉及一些知识点必须提前讲述，故做此序。</p><h5 id="🧩-pug-文件："><a href="#🧩-pug-文件：" class="headerlink" title="🧩 .pug 文件："></a>🧩 <code>.pug</code> 文件：</h5><p>定义页面结构（HTML）</p><p>Pug 是 HTML 的模板引擎，在 Butterfly 中主要用于定义页面结构。</p><p>你创建的 <code>.pug</code> 文件常用于：✅ 加载动画模块</p><h5 id="🎨-styl-文件："><a href="#🎨-styl-文件：" class="headerlink" title="🎨 .styl 文件："></a>🎨 <code>.styl</code> 文件：</h5><p>定义样式和动画（CSS）</p><p>Stylus 是 CSS 的预处理器，Butterfly 使用它来书写主题样式。</p><p>你创建的 <code>.styl</code> 文件，一般用于：✅ 为加载动画编写动画效果和布局</p><h4 id="一，修改loading-pug"><a href="#一，修改loading-pug" class="headerlink" title="一，修改loading.pug"></a>一，修改loading.pug</h4><p>修改[Blogroot]\themes\butterfly\layout\includes\loading\loading.pug，下面代码中提供了7种款式，可自行选择要的主题哦。</p><p>注意奥，我的butterfly的版本是<strong>Butterfly 5.3.5</strong>，已经不是这个文件了，而是”butterfly\layout\includes\loading\fullpage-loading.pug”</p><p>修改前(主题默认旋转盒子)：</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">#loading-box</span><br><span class="line">  .loading-left-bg</span><br><span class="line">  .loading-right-bg</span><br><span class="line">  .spinner-box</span><br><span class="line">    .configure-border-1</span><br><span class="line">      .configure-core</span><br><span class="line">    .configure-border-2</span><br><span class="line">      .configure-core</span><br><span class="line">    .loading-word= _p(&#x27;loading&#x27;)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>修改替换（直接替换上面那段就好了）：</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">if theme.preloader.enable</span><br><span class="line">  case theme.preloader.load_style    </span><br><span class="line">    when &#x27;gear&#x27;</span><br><span class="line">      include ./load_style/gear.pug</span><br><span class="line">    when &#x27;ironheart&#x27;</span><br><span class="line">      include ./load_style/ironheart.pug</span><br><span class="line">    when &#x27;scarecrow&#x27;</span><br><span class="line">      include ./load_style/scarecrow.pug</span><br><span class="line">    when &#x27;triangles&#x27;</span><br><span class="line">      include ./load_style/triangles.pug</span><br><span class="line">    when &#x27;wizard&#x27;</span><br><span class="line">      include ./load_style/wizard.pug</span><br><span class="line">    when &#x27;image&#x27;</span><br><span class="line">      include ./load_style/image.pug</span><br><span class="line">    default</span><br><span class="line">      include ./load_style/default.pug</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>此处第一行的if用于判断preloader功能是否打开。</p><p>下面的case和when则是根据配置项的内容加载指定的页面元素。default表示使用butterfly自带的默认旋转盒子动画。</p><h4 id="二，pug文件编写"><a href="#二，pug文件编写" class="headerlink" title="二，pug文件编写"></a>二，pug文件编写</h4><p>接下来进行pug文件的编写</p><h5 id="1-default"><a href="#1-default" class="headerlink" title="1.default"></a>1.default</h5><p>新建[Blogroot]\themes\butterfly\layout\includes\loading\load_style\default.pug<br>这是默认动画。</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">#loading-box</span><br><span class="line">  .loading-left-bg</span><br><span class="line">  .loading-right-bg</span><br><span class="line">  .spinner-box</span><br><span class="line">    .configure-border-1</span><br><span class="line">      .configure-core</span><br><span class="line">    .configure-border-2</span><br><span class="line">      .configure-core</span><br><span class="line">    .loading-word= _p(&#x27;loading&#x27;)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h5 id="2-gear"><a href="#2-gear" class="headerlink" title="2. gear"></a>2. gear</h5><p>新建[Blogroot]\themes\butterfly\layout\includes\loading\load_style\gear.pug</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">#loading-box</span><br><span class="line">  .gear-loader</span><br><span class="line">    .gear-loader_overlay</span><br><span class="line">    .gear-loader_cogs</span><br><span class="line">      .gear-loader_cogs__top</span><br><span class="line">        .gear-top_part</span><br><span class="line">        .gear-top_part</span><br><span class="line">        .gear-top_part</span><br><span class="line">        .gear-top_hole</span><br><span class="line">      .gear-loader_cogs__left</span><br><span class="line">        .gear-left_part</span><br><span class="line">        .gear-left_part</span><br><span class="line">        .gear-left_part</span><br><span class="line">        .gear-left_hole</span><br><span class="line">      .gear-loader_cogs__bottom</span><br><span class="line">        .gear-bottom_part</span><br><span class="line">        .gear-bottom_part</span><br><span class="line">        .gear-bottom_part</span><br><span class="line">        .gear-bottom_hole</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h5 id="3-image"><a href="#3-image" class="headerlink" title="3.image"></a>3.image</h5><p>新建[Blogroot]\themes\butterfly\layout\includes\loading\load_style\image.pug</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">- var loadimage = theme.preloader.load_image ? theme.preloader.load_image : theme.error_img.post_page</span><br><span class="line">#loading-box</span><br><span class="line">  .loading-left-bg</span><br><span class="line">  .loading-right-bg</span><br><span class="line">  img.load-image(src=url_for(loadimage) alt=&#x27;&#x27;)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h5 id="4-ironheart"><a href="#4-ironheart" class="headerlink" title="4.ironheart"></a>4.ironheart</h5><p>新建[Blogroot]\themes\butterfly\layout\includes\loading\load_style\ironheart.pug</p><p>这是钢铁之心加载动画。</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">#loading-box</span><br><span class="line">  .loading-left-bg</span><br><span class="line">  .loading-right-bg</span><br><span class="line">  .iron-container.iron-circle</span><br><span class="line">    .iron-box1.iron-circle.iron-center</span><br><span class="line">    .iron-box2.iron-circle.iron-center</span><br><span class="line">    .iron-box3.iron-circle.iron-center</span><br><span class="line">    .iron-box4.iron-circle.iron-center</span><br><span class="line">    .iron-box5.iron-circle.iron-center</span><br><span class="line">    .iron-box6.iron-circle</span><br><span class="line">      .iron-coil(style=&#x27;--i: 0&#x27;)</span><br><span class="line">      .iron-coil(style=&#x27;--i: 1&#x27;)</span><br><span class="line">      .iron-coil(style=&#x27;--i: 2&#x27;)</span><br><span class="line">      .iron-coil(style=&#x27;--i: 3&#x27;)</span><br><span class="line">      .iron-coil(style=&#x27;--i: 4&#x27;)</span><br><span class="line">      .iron-coil(style=&#x27;--i: 5&#x27;)</span><br><span class="line">      .iron-coil(style=&#x27;--i: 6&#x27;)</span><br><span class="line">      .iron-coil(style=&#x27;--i: 7&#x27;)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h5 id="5-scarecrow"><a href="#5-scarecrow" class="headerlink" title="5.scarecrow"></a>5.scarecrow</h5><p>新建[Blogroot]\themes\butterfly\layout\includes\loading\load_style\scarecrow.pug</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">#loading-box</span><br><span class="line">  .loading-left-bg</span><br><span class="line">  .loading-right-bg</span><br><span class="line">  .scarecrow</span><br><span class="line">    .scarecrow__hat</span><br><span class="line">      .scarecrow__ribbon</span><br><span class="line">    .scarecrow__head</span><br><span class="line">      .scarecrow__eye</span><br><span class="line">      .scarecrow__eye</span><br><span class="line">      .scarecrow__mouth</span><br><span class="line">      .scarecrow__pipe</span><br><span class="line">    .scarecrow__body</span><br><span class="line">      .scarecrow__glove.scarecrow__glove--l</span><br><span class="line">      .scarecrow__sleeve.scarecrow__sleeve--l</span><br><span class="line">      .scarecrow__bow</span><br><span class="line">      .scarecrow__shirt</span><br><span class="line">      .scarecrow__coat</span><br><span class="line">      .scarecrow__waistcoat</span><br><span class="line">      .scarecrow__sleeve.scarecrow__sleeve--r</span><br><span class="line">      .scarecrow__glove.scarecrow__glove--r</span><br><span class="line">      .scarecrow__coattails</span><br><span class="line">      .scarecrow__pants</span><br><span class="line">    .scarecrow__arms</span><br><span class="line">    .scarecrow__leg   </span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h5 id="6-triangles"><a href="#6-triangles" class="headerlink" title="6.triangles"></a>6.triangles</h5><p>新建[Blogroot]\themes\butterfly\layout\includes\loading\load_style\triangles.pug</p><p>这是旋转三角加载动画。</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">#loading-box</span><br><span class="line">  .triangles-wrap</span><br><span class="line">    .triangles-eiz</span><br><span class="line">    .triangles-seiz</span><br><span class="line">    .triangles-sei</span><br><span class="line">    .triangles-fei</span><br><span class="line">    .triangles-feir</span><br><span class="line">    .triangles-trei</span><br><span class="line">    .triangles-dvai</span><br><span class="line">    .triangles-ein</span><br><span class="line">    .triangles-zero</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h5 id="7-wizard"><a href="#7-wizard" class="headerlink" title="7.wizard"></a>7.wizard</h5><p>新建[Blogroot]\themes\butterfly\layout\includes\loading\load_style\wizard.pug</p><p>这是巫师施法加载动画。（我现在使用的就是这个啦）</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">#loading-box</span><br><span class="line">  .loading-left-bg</span><br><span class="line">  .loading-right-bg</span><br><span class="line">  .wizard-scene</span><br><span class="line">    .wizard-objects</span><br><span class="line">      .wizard-square</span><br><span class="line">      .wizard-circle</span><br><span class="line">      .wizard-triangle</span><br><span class="line">    .wizard</span><br><span class="line">      .wizard-body</span><br><span class="line">      .wizard-right-arm</span><br><span class="line">        .wizard-right-hand</span><br><span class="line">      .wizard-left-arm</span><br><span class="line">        .wizard-left-hand</span><br><span class="line">      .wizard-head</span><br><span class="line">        .wizard-beard</span><br><span class="line">        .wizard-face</span><br><span class="line">          .wizard-adds</span><br><span class="line">        .wizard-hat</span><br><span class="line">          .wizard-hat-of-the-hat</span><br><span class="line">          .wizard-four-point-star.--first</span><br><span class="line">          .wizard-four-point-star.--second</span><br><span class="line">          .wizard-four-point-star.--third</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="三、修改loading-styl"><a href="#三、修改loading-styl" class="headerlink" title="三、修改loading.styl"></a>三、修改loading.styl</h4><p>修改[Blogroot]\themes\butterfly\source\css_layout\loading.styl</p><p>修改前（默认旋转盒子动画的样式）：</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br><span class="line">32</span><br><span class="line">33</span><br><span class="line">34</span><br><span class="line">35</span><br><span class="line">36</span><br><span class="line">37</span><br><span class="line">38</span><br><span class="line">39</span><br><span class="line">40</span><br><span class="line">41</span><br><span class="line">42</span><br><span class="line">43</span><br><span class="line">44</span><br><span class="line">45</span><br><span class="line">46</span><br><span class="line">47</span><br><span class="line">48</span><br><span class="line">49</span><br><span class="line">50</span><br><span class="line">51</span><br><span class="line">52</span><br><span class="line">53</span><br><span class="line">54</span><br><span class="line">55</span><br><span class="line">56</span><br><span class="line">57</span><br><span class="line">58</span><br><span class="line">59</span><br><span class="line">60</span><br><span class="line">61</span><br><span class="line">62</span><br><span class="line">63</span><br><span class="line">64</span><br><span class="line">65</span><br><span class="line">66</span><br><span class="line">67</span><br><span class="line">68</span><br><span class="line">69</span><br><span class="line">70</span><br><span class="line">71</span><br><span class="line">72</span><br><span class="line">73</span><br><span class="line">74</span><br><span class="line">75</span><br><span class="line">76</span><br><span class="line">77</span><br><span class="line">78</span><br><span class="line">79</span><br><span class="line">80</span><br><span class="line">81</span><br><span class="line">82</span><br><span class="line">83</span><br><span class="line">84</span><br><span class="line">85</span><br><span class="line">86</span><br><span class="line">87</span><br><span class="line">88</span><br><span class="line">89</span><br><span class="line">90</span><br><span class="line">91</span><br><span class="line">92</span><br><span class="line">93</span><br><span class="line">94</span><br><span class="line">95</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">if hexo-config(&#x27;preloader&#x27;)</span><br><span class="line">  .loading-bg</span><br><span class="line">    position: fixed</span><br><span class="line">    z-index: 1000</span><br><span class="line">    width: 50%</span><br><span class="line">    height: 100%</span><br><span class="line">    background-color: var(--preloader-bg)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">  #loading-box</span><br><span class="line">    .loading-left-bg</span><br><span class="line">      @extend .loading-bg</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    .loading-right-bg</span><br><span class="line">      @extend .loading-bg</span><br><span class="line">      right: 0</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    .spinner-box</span><br><span class="line">      position: fixed</span><br><span class="line">      z-index: 1001</span><br><span class="line">      display: flex</span><br><span class="line">      justify-content: center</span><br><span class="line">      align-items: center</span><br><span class="line">      width: 100%</span><br><span class="line">      height: 100vh</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">      .configure-border-1</span><br><span class="line">        position: absolute</span><br><span class="line">        padding: 3px</span><br><span class="line">        width: 115px</span><br><span class="line">        height: 115px</span><br><span class="line">        background: #ffab91</span><br><span class="line">        animation: configure-clockwise 3s ease-in-out 0s infinite alternate</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">      .configure-border-2</span><br><span class="line">        left: -115px</span><br><span class="line">        padding: 3px</span><br><span class="line">        width: 115px</span><br><span class="line">        height: 115px</span><br><span class="line">        background: rgb(63, 249, 220)</span><br><span class="line">        transform: rotate(45deg)</span><br><span class="line">        animation: configure-xclockwise 3s ease-in-out 0s infinite alternate</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">      .loading-word</span><br><span class="line">        position: absolute</span><br><span class="line">        color: var(--preloader-color)</span><br><span class="line">        font-size: .8rem</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">      .configure-core</span><br><span class="line">        width: 100%</span><br><span class="line">        height: 100%</span><br><span class="line">        background-color: var(--preloader-bg)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    &amp;.loaded</span><br><span class="line">      .loading-left-bg</span><br><span class="line">        transition: all .5s</span><br><span class="line">        transform: translate(-100%, 0)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">      .loading-right-bg</span><br><span class="line">        transition: all .5s</span><br><span class="line">        transform: translate(100%, 0)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">      .spinner-box</span><br><span class="line">        display: none</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">  @keyframes configure-clockwise</span><br><span class="line">    0%</span><br><span class="line">      transform: rotate(0)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    25%</span><br><span class="line">      transform: rotate(90deg)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    50%</span><br><span class="line">      transform: rotate(180deg)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    75%</span><br><span class="line">      transform: rotate(270deg)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    100%</span><br><span class="line">      transform: rotate(360deg)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">  @keyframes configure-xclockwise</span><br><span class="line">    0%</span><br><span class="line">      transform: rotate(45deg)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    25%</span><br><span class="line">      transform: rotate(-45deg)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    50%</span><br><span class="line">      transform: rotate(-135deg)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    75%</span><br><span class="line">      transform: rotate(-225deg)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    100%</span><br><span class="line">      transform: rotate(-315deg)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>复制以下代码替换全部内容：</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">if hexo-config(&#x27;preloader.enable&#x27;)</span><br><span class="line">  if hexo-config(&#x27;preloader.load_style&#x27;) == &#x27;gear&#x27;</span><br><span class="line">    @import &#x27;./_load_style/gear&#x27;</span><br><span class="line">  else if hexo-config(&#x27;preloader.load_style&#x27;) == &#x27;ironheart&#x27;</span><br><span class="line">    @import &#x27;./_load_style/ironheart&#x27;</span><br><span class="line">  else if hexo-config(&#x27;preloader.load_style&#x27;) == &#x27;scarecrow&#x27;</span><br><span class="line">    @import &#x27;./_load_style/scarecrow&#x27;</span><br><span class="line">  else if hexo-config(&#x27;preloader.load_style&#x27;) == &#x27;triangles&#x27;</span><br><span class="line">    @import &#x27;./_load_style/triangles&#x27;</span><br><span class="line">  else if hexo-config(&#x27;preloader.load_style&#x27;) == &#x27;wizard&#x27;</span><br><span class="line">    @import &#x27;./_load_style/wizard&#x27;</span><br><span class="line">  else if hexo-config(&#x27;preloader.load_style&#x27;) == &#x27;image&#x27;</span><br><span class="line">    @import &#x27;./_load_style/image&#x27;</span><br><span class="line">  else</span><br><span class="line">    @import &#x27;./_load_style/default&#x27;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>几个if的判断机制与loading.pug类似，都是根据配置项来决定加载的样式。且默认使用旋转盒子动画。</p><h4 id="四、创建动画样式模板文件夹"><a href="#四、创建动画样式模板文件夹" class="headerlink" title="四、创建动画样式模板文件夹"></a>四、创建动画样式模板文件夹</h4><p>新建动画样式模板存放的文件夹，如无特别提示，所有动画样式均存放在[Blogroot]\themes\butterfly\source\css_load_style\目录下</p><h5 id="1-default-1"><a href="#1-default-1" class="headerlink" title="1.default"></a>1.default</h5><p>新建[Blogroot]\themes\butterfly\source\css_load_style\default.sty</p><hr><p>昨天回学校和sing见面，虽然只分别一个多星期，但我总感觉我们分别了好长时间，明天sing就要做一个小手术了，虽然是小手术，也去了最好的医院，但是我多多少少还是有些担心，让我心疼的是，术前还是要禁食禁水，而且是全麻，因为我也没有经历过全麻，不由恐惧起来，sing要被割掉一块肉，听说今天抽血被抽了好几罐，更是心疼。想起昨日黏在一起，更是久久萦绕心间。今晚的思念恐怕更加浓烈。sing做完手术后想去看望一下她，我想去，现在如果可以，现在就想去。</p><hr><p>sing做完手术了，刚开始听到她的声音感觉好虚弱了，我真的想如果此时我在她的身旁就好了，而且麻醉的时候喉咙被塞住，弄得特别不舒服，流程很多，医生自己也搞不清，有种被耍来耍去的感觉，周天我要去看看她，我好后悔没有请假，陪在她身边，当她说出：“不要担心啦，这只是个小手术”。我永远无法忘记sing坚强而又不愿让我担心的这一刻，那一刻我也意识到，sing真是受苦了&#x2F;(ㄒoㄒ)&#x2F;~~。</p><div class="social-share"></div><!--  css & js --><link rel="stylesheet" href="dist/css/share.min.css"><script src="dist/js/social-share.min.js"></script><script src="https://giscus.app/client.js"        data-repo="laihaida123/comment_save"        data-repo-id="R_kgDOPMVXJA"        data-category="Announcements"        data-category-id="DIC_kwDOPMVXJM4Cs7uV"        data-mapping="title"        data-strict="0"        data-reactions-enabled="1"        data-emit-metadata="0"        data-input-position="top"        data-theme="preferred_color_scheme"        data-lang="zh-CN"        data-loading="lazy"        crossorigin="anonymous"        async></script>]]></content>
    
    
